212
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:23,990
Hey!

213
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:26,050
Wait for me!

214
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,820
Hey!

215
00:12:31,940 --> 00:12:36,940
My name is Luffy! I'm not mad
about you spitting on me anymore!

216
00:12:41,690 --> 00:12:43,450
Why are you laughing?!

217
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:48,370
He only spilled some booze on me.
It's nothing worth getting mad over.

218
00:12:48,370 --> 00:12:51,890
It's nothing worth getting mad
over. Let's become friends!

219
00:12:52,450 --> 00:12:53,830
