Easy, easy, boss.

258
00:17:12,260 --> 00:17:14,800
Where were you?!

259
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:17,800
Easy, easy. Where were you
and what were you doing?

260
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:21,680
I've been chased by wolves
at the bottom of the valley.

261
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:24,980
What were you doing at
the bottom of the valley?

262
00:17:27,230 --> 00:17:31,690
--Anyway, it's nice that you're okay.
--Yeah.

263
00:17:31,690 --> 00:17:35,700
It's not okay! The pest came back!

264
00:17:36,740 --> 00:17:41,530
Why don't you go to bed tonight?
You gotta work from tomorrow!

265
00:17:41,530 --> 00:17:42,490
Already?

266
00:17:51,620 --> 00:17:53,050
What's up?

267
00:17:53,050 --> 00:17:55,420
Are you gonna go somewhere today, Ace?

268
00:17:55,420 --> 00:17:59,430
Take me with you! Let's become friends!

269
00:17:59,970 --> 00:18:01,260
Wait for me!

270
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:03,810
Boss! He's going after Ace again!

271
00:18:04,520 --> 00:18:08,520
Hey! You gotta do chores around the house!

272
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:12,110
No thank you!

273
00:18:12,690 --> 00:18:15,340
You little shit! You're out of control!

274
00:18:15,340 --> 00:18:16,690
Easy, easy, boss.

275
00:18:16,690 --> 00:18:19,160
--Bring him back right now!
--Yes, ma'am.

276
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:21,370
Hey!

277
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:46,380
Ace!

278
00:18:51,810 --> 00:18:54,960
Ace! Let's become friends!

279
00:19:03,490 --> 00:19:05,080
The 8th day...

280
00:19:05,950 --> 00:19:07,260
Ace!

281
00:19:07,260 --> 00:19:08,960
Wait for me!

282
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:09,870
Boss!

283
00:19:09,870 --> 00:19:11,920
Work, you little shit!

284
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,080
It's no use...

285
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:14,840
--Bring him back!
--Yes, ma'am.

286
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:16,670
I'm not gonna lose you today!

287
00:19:18,670 --> 00:19:20,180
I can do that!

288
00:19:23,890 --> 00:19:25,930
Let's become friends!

289
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:31,560
10 days have passed...

290
00:19:31,560 --> 00:19:34,440
--Luffy!
--He's gone already...

291
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:36,110
Look for him!

292
00:19:40,360 --> 00:19:42,910
He kept going after Ace and losing him.

293
00:19:46,280 --> 00:19:48,840
But it went on everyday.

294
00:19:48,840 --> 00:19:50,460
Ace!

295
00:19:58,450 --> 00:20:00,090
1 month...

296
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:02,630
2 months...

297
00:20:03,040 --> 00:20:04,670
Ace!

298
00:20:04,670 --> 00:20:08,230
No matter if it rained and was windy...

299
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:12,560
Ace!

300
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:16,150
Luffy kept going after Ace desperately.

301
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:21,950
Luffy is chasing Ace again?!

302
00:20:21,950 --> 00:20:26,220
How does he never learn after
getting hurt so many times?

303
00:20:26,220 --> 00:20:28,990
Damn! He has to stop making me worry!

304
00:20:28,990 --> 00:20:30,960
So you're worrying.

305
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:33,920
N-No way! Stop talking nonsense!

306
00:20:36,250 --> 00:20:38,530
A bee-hive fell on me.

307
00:20:39,970 --> 00:20:41,050
Who are you?

308
00:20:44,690 --> 00:20:46,800
Ace!

309
00:20:54,730 --> 00:20:58,440
Ace! Hey!

310
00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:02,290
I can't believe he's coming
this far. He's so persistent.

311
00:21:04,110 --> 00:21:05,260
Oh crap!

312
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:10,420
Damn! I lost him again! Ace runs so fast!

313
00:21:12,210 --> 00:21:13,410
Is it Ace?!

314
00:21:21,500 --> 00:21:26,380
That's the beast of Mt.
Corvo! No one can beat it!

315
00:21:28,930 --> 00:21:31,510
Why is he not running?! It's gonna eat him!

316
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:35,640
I-I feel weak at the knees!

317
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:37,310
That fool!

318
00:22:44,450 --> 00:22:48,990
Now, Luffy had been chasing Ace for 3
months with cuts and bruises all over...

319
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:58,790
It's the end of the forest.

320
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:15,950
What is this place?

321
00:23:25,470 --> 00:23:28,630
Discarded junk lies around everywhere,
and smoke fills the air.

322
00:23:28,630 --> 00:23:31,300
This is Gray Terminal, a town of outlaws.

323
00:23:32,050 --> 00:23:34,720
Ace once took charge of the thugs here,

324
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:38,020
amassing funds in order to
become a pirate someday.

325
00:23:38,020 --> 00:23:41,100
Along with one other friend...

326
00:23:41,100 --> 00:23:42,480
On the next episode of One Piece!

327
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:45,270
"Here Comes Sabo! The Boy
at the Gray Terminal!"

328
00:23:45,270 --> 00:23:47,820
I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
